title: A home above!
posting_body: ['Text 1274C to my cell for more info!', 'AUSTIN’S SKIES HAVE A NEW COMPANION.', 'LIFT YOUR GAZE TO ALEXAN, A BOLD STATEMENT FOR THE DISCERNING FEW', 'WHO CHOOSE TO LIVE HERE.', 'OFFERING AN ELEVATED SENSE OF PERMANENCE, THIS STRIKING 30-STORY TOWER BOASTING AN UNHEARD OF AMENITY LIST, CAN BE THE PLACE THAT YOU CALL HOME.', 'THE NEW STANDARD OF LIVING.', 'Stunning architecture that makes a bold statement.', 'An enviable array of amenities that cater to your every need.', 'A personal space with the extra touches that set it apart.', 'And a location from where you can get anywhere.', 'Alexan Waterloo is the new standard of living.', 'OUR AMENITIES', 'A HOME ABOVE,', 'INSIDE AND OUT', 'Our well-appointed apartments feature an open floor plan, wood flooring, high end finishes like granite countertops, stainless steel appliances featuring French door refrigerators, and contemporary cabinetry.', 'Bathrooms are complete with luxury spa shower/tub combos, rain shower heads and back-lit LED mirrors**.', 'To take things even higher, Alexan has penthouses offering even more.', 'VIEW FEATURES', 'VISIT US', 'Panoramic views of Austin.', 'High-end interior designs.', 'Amenities that cater to your every need.', 'Find the lifestyle you deserve at Alexan Waterloo.', 'SCHEDULE YOUR TOUR TODAY', 'GET VIP ACCESS', 'Join our VIP list for exclusive updates.', 'We invite guests to park on the second level of the Alexan parking garage.', 'Please take elevators to the Lobby level to be greeted by our Leasing team.', 'Welcome home to Alexan!', 'Contentment begins at home, especially when you choose the A3 one-bedroom at Alexan Waterloo.', 'Discover the serenity pure luxury provides with...']
